
GSTK is a stand-alone wish with GS-extensions

GS is a Graphics Interface for Erlang


This version of gstk uses:

- Tcl7.6	ftp://ftp.sunlabs.com/pub/tcl/tcl7.6.tar.gz
- Tk4.2		ftp://ftp.sunlabs.com/pub/tcl/tk4.2.tar.gz
- Plus Patches	ftp://ftp.nici.kun.nl/pub/tkpvm/tcl7.6plus.patch.gz
		ftp://ftp.nici.kun.nl/pub/tkpvm/tk4.2plus.patch.gz


INSTALLATION: 

make [OS]	where OS is [solaris2|sunos4|x86]. This will build
		gstk, wrap and killer.  The default value is solaris2.

make install	This will install gstk, wrap and killer in GS_BIN_DIR
		(see Makefile).  To set GS_BIN_DIR change the Makefile
		or use: make GS_BIN_DIR=/where/you/want install


FEEDBACK:

Comments and Bug reports can be sent to: bugs@erlang.ericsson.se 

